Warning: We are making changes, in preparation for Mountain Lion, and thus things might get broken onc in a while, 
and when that happens, then we want you to use: https://github.com/RevoGirl/RevoBoot/issues
and let us know. Thank you!

RevoBoot can to be configured specifically for your hardware so please start by reading our WiKi at:

https://github.com/blackosx/RevoBuilder/wiki/Using-RevoBuilder

We also have a configuration README available at:

https://github.com/RevoGirl/RevoBoot/blob/master/i386/config/README

There's also RevoBuilder (a great tool for first starters) over at:

https://github.com/blackosx/RevoBuilder/wiki/Using-RevoBuilder

And brand-spanking-new (since early July 2011) the RevoGirl blog over at:

http://revogirl.wordpress.com/ 
